Marahi dan usir dia.

252
00:14:16,021 --> 00:14:18,482
Aku tak bisa.

253
00:14:18,566 --> 00:14:19,483
Diam.

254
00:14:19,567 --> 00:14:20,818
Tutup mulutmu. Pergilah.

255
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,361
Sakit.

256
00:14:28,784 --> 00:14:30,494
Demamku tak kunjung mereda.

257
00:14:31,453 --> 00:14:35,416
Kalau begini, aku tidak bisa pindah
dalam beberapa hari.

258
00:14:36,083 --> 00:14:37,001
Siapa kau?

259
00:14:40,504 --> 00:14:42,006
Sedang apa kau di sini?

260
00:14:42,089 --> 00:14:44,216
Rumah ini...

261
00:14:45,593 --> 00:14:48,387
Ini markas rahasia kami.

262
00:14:49,889 --> 00:14:50,806
Ternyata kau.

263
00:14:51,140 --> 00:14:53,475
Bukankah kau anak yang membaca
Daftar Pahlawan?

264
00:14:55,477 --> 00:14:57,187
Kau paman yang waktu itu.

265
00:14:57,271 --> 00:14:59,481
Bukankah sudah kubilang,
aku bukan "paman"?

266
00:15:00,107 --> 00:15:01,108
Kau butuh apa?

267
00:15:01,358 --> 00:15:02,776
Begini...

268
00:15:03,944 --> 00:15:08,407
Tolong tinggalkan rumah ini.

269
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:12,703
Kenapa aku diusir?

270
00:15:14,496 --> 00:15:17,708
Karena semua orang
memintaku memberitahumu.

271
00:15:17,791 --> 00:15:18,876
Mereka teman-temanmu?

272
00:15:18,959 --> 00:15:20,377
Tolak saja.

273
00:15:20,794 --> 00:15:22,046
Tapi...

274
00:15:22,129 --> 00:15:23,797
Jangan menangis. Menyebalkan.

275
00:15:26,008 --> 00:15:27,384
Jangan khawatir.

276
00:15:27,551 --> 00:15:29,595
Aku akan pergi setelah beberapa saat.

277
00:15:30,429 --> 00:15:32,389
Jika mereka keberatan,

278
00:15:32,681 --> 00:15:34,725
suruh temanmu datang.

279
00:15:35,059 --> 00:15:36,727
Kau paham, Nak?

280
00:15:36,936 --> 00:15:38,187
Ya.

281
00:15:42,024 --> 00:15:44,485
Biar kuajari solusinya.

282
00:15:45,194 --> 00:15:47,571
Akan kuajarkan cara
agar kau tak diremehkan.

283
00:15:48,822 --> 00:15:50,658
Ya, aku ingin tahu.

284
00:15:51,617 --> 00:15:53,744
Tareo lama sekali.

285
00:15:53,827 --> 00:15:55,704
Terjadi sesuatukah?

286
00:15:55,871 --> 00:15:57,331
Anak-anak, menjauh.

287
00:15:58,957 --> 00:16:00,542
Dia Death Gatling.

288
00:16:00,751 --> 00:16:02,169
Di sini berbahaya.

289
00:16:02,336 --> 00:16:04,755
Smile Man dan Stinger juga di sini.

290
00:16:04,838 --> 00:16:06,048
Luar biasa.

291
00:16:06,298 --> 00:16:08,634
Sekumpulan pahlawan.

292
00:16:09,301 --> 00:16:12,471
Pemburu Pahlawan yang terluka
ada di dalam rumah itu, 'kan?

293
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:13,555
Ya.

294
00:16:14,056 --> 00:16:15,808
Pemburu Pahlawan, Garou.

295
00:16:16,266 --> 00:16:19,228
Kini giliran kami memburumu.

296
00:16:19,353 --> 00:16:22,106
Ada sesuatu di dalam?

297
00:16:22,898 --> 00:16:25,192
Ada monster kejam di dalam.

298
00:16:25,484 --> 00:16:26,902
Tolong segera pergi.

299
00:16:27,653 --> 00:16:29,363
Baik.

300
00:16:29,488 --> 00:16:30,656
Gawat.

301
00:16:30,739 --> 00:16:33,242
Kita harus apa?
Kita menyuruh Tareo masuk sendiri.

302
00:16:33,325 --> 00:16:36,286
Para pahlawan sudah tiba.
Kurasa dia akan baik-baik saja.

303
00:16:36,370 --> 00:16:37,329
Kau benar.

304
00:16:38,288 --> 00:16:40,207
Jika kau tak mau diremehkan orang lain,

305
00:16:40,374 --> 00:16:42,418
atau disuruh-suruh orang lain,

306
00:16:43,419 --> 00:16:45,170
jadilah lebih kuat.

307
00:16:46,213 --> 00:16:47,256
Bagaimana?

308
00:16:47,506 --> 00:16:48,716
Solusi yang bagus, 'kan?

309
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:51,218
Bukankah itu jelas?

310
00:16:55,556 --> 00:16:57,391
Ya.

311
00:16:57,474 --> 00:17:00,019
Apa? Kau sudah tahu itu, 'kan?

312
00:17:01,729 --> 00:17:03,522
Lukaku sakit setiap kali aku tertawa.

313
00:17:03,731 --> 00:17:05,315
Paman baik-baik saja?

314
00:17:05,399 --> 00:17:06,400
Jangan khawatir.

315
00:17:06,775 --> 00:17:09,278
Cukup bicaranya.
Kau harus pulang sekarang.

316
00:17:09,737 --> 00:17:11,155
Ya.

317
00:17:13,365 --> 00:17:14,616
Dia membuka pintu.

318
00:17:14,783 --> 00:17:15,701
Dengar baik-baik.

319
00:17:15,951 --> 00:17:18,704
Tembak begitu kau melihat tubuhnya.

320
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:20,706
Aku dikepung.

321
00:17:20,789 --> 00:17:21,707
Tunggu.

322
00:17:22,666 --> 00:17:26,253
Karena aku sudah beri solusi bagus,
izinkan aku membaca Daftar Pahlawan-mu.

323
00:17:26,628 --> 00:17:27,755
Kau membawanya, 'kan?

324
00:17:28,714 --> 00:17:30,132
Ada padaku.

325
00:17:30,382 --> 00:17:31,425
Tapi kenapa?

326
00:17:31,508 --> 00:17:33,343
Karena aku membutuhkannya sekarang.

327
00:17:33,427 --> 00:17:34,970
Ya, aku tak keberatan.

328
