Buku ini berisi semua informasi
mengenai pahlawan, 'kan?

330
00:17:42,269 --> 00:17:45,355
Ya, tapi tak semua orang termasuk.

331
00:17:45,439 --> 00:17:46,482
Begitu rupanya.

332
00:17:51,779 --> 00:17:52,905
DEATH GATLING, STINGER

333
00:17:52,988 --> 00:17:53,989
Di barisan depan...

334
