SMILE MAN, WILD HORN

335
00:17:55,074 --> 00:17:55,991
Ada empat orang.

336
00:17:56,492 --> 00:17:57,409
Di barisan belakang...

337
00:17:57,493 --> 00:17:58,327
GLASSES, CHAIN'N'TOAD

338
00:17:58,410 --> 00:17:59,328
Ada dua orang.

339
00:17:59,661 --> 00:18:00,579
